==========================================================
Note:
1. create soft links:
   ln -sf /usr/local/sbin/waagent /usr/sbin/waagent
   ln -sf /usr/local/sbin/waagent2.0 /usr/sbin/waagent2.0

2. To enable waagent, add the following line to rc.conf:

waagent_enable="YES"

This will make sure waagent is started at boot.
==========================================================
